'''Callum Greene''' ([[22 February]], [[1971]]) is a British producer. He was credited as executive producer in ''[[The Hobbit: The Desolation of Smaug]]'' and he is one of the executive producers of the first season of ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Rings of Power]]'' series by [[Amazon.com Incorporated|Amazon]].<ref>{{webcite|author=|articleurl=https://www.imdb.com/name/nm0338696/?ref_=nmbio_bio_nm|articlename=Callum Greene|dated=|website=IMDB|accessed=3 December 2022}}</ref>
